WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:05.540 --> 00:00:09.639
This video is to show you the power and innovation of the new special edition of the TELO PINCO.

00:00:09.639 --> 00:00:13.479
We have identified some problems common to every athlete:

00:00:13.479 --> 00:00:15.699
sinusitis, allergy to wate

00:00:15.699 --> 00:00:19.800
r and the impossibility of maintaining the speed

00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:20.980
reached with the acceleration of the start.

00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:24.109
We then placed two targets: to combat athletes' allergy to water

00:00:24.109 --> 00:00:26.329
and to maintain top speed

00:00:26.329 --> 00:00:29.739
Now I show you five features of our new Kayak

00:00:29.739 --> 00:00:30.349
absolutely revolutionary.

00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:36.920
The first characteristic is the absence of the prow!

00:00:36.920 --> 00:00:39.100
For years we have built boats with prows,

00:00:39.100 --> 00:00:43.480
able to cutting the water, disregarding the power that this could give the boat.

00:00:43.480 --> 00:00:46.890
After years of research we have identified a successful strategy:

00:00:46.890 --> 00:00:48.580
to reverse the hull and deck.

00:00:48.580 --> 00:00:50.960
We have built so the best not-prow of the last 901 years.

00:00:53.130 --> 00:00:56.290
when the boat picks up speed, the prow gives on the hull a force

00:00:56.290 --> 00:00:58.780
that alters the mass of the boat.

00:00:58.780 --> 00:01:02.109
For Einstein's law the speed of light squared

00:01:02.109 --> 00:01:03.969
is equal to the energy divided by the mass.

00:01:03.969 --> 00:01:07.979
The mass thus tending to zero, the speed tends to increase and, in cases of high wave,

00:01:07.979 --> 00:01:10.220
you may even reach the speed of light.

00:01:11.799 --> 00:01:12.700
The new pool,

00:01:12.700 --> 00:01:16.210
more streamlined, cancel any kind of friction with the air and,

00:01:16.210 --> 00:01:21.320
due to its amplitude allows the cultivation of peonies and small tubers.

00:01:21.320 --> 00:01:25.200
The cockpit of the new PINCO is designed to give maximum comfort to the athlete.

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:28.810
That's why the boat is made of 70 different sizes

00:01:28.810 --> 00:01:33.450
from xsupermegaess to iperarciextralarge

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.979
How often during a race you happen to have a salami

00:01:37.979 --> 00:01:40.479
but you can not cut it because you don't have a knife?

00:01:40.600 --> 00:01:45.359
the new rudder is taken directly from the series of three Miracle Blade. 
It allows you to slice the logs, seaweed, fish and baobab

00:01:45.359 --> 00:01:49.289
that often fit in the rudder.
 Due to the formula Extract-Easy

00:01:49.289 --> 00:01:54.200
you can use it to cut the salami kept in the boat!

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:03.780
This boat is the result of efforts of the TELO team,

00:02:03.780 --> 00:02:05.880
who worked tirelessly for you.

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:08.910
All the tests we performed have revealed

00:02:08.910 --> 00:02:10.910
to us that this is the best boat we've ever built.

